Feature: Hotel Booking In Adactin Application 

Scenario: Login page
Given user Launch The Application 
When user Enter The Username In Username Field
And user Enter The Password In Password Field
Then user Click On Login Button And It Navigates To The Search Hotel Page

Scenario: Search Hotel Page
When user Select The Hotel Location 
And user Select The Hotel Hotels
And user Select The Hotel RoomType
And user Select The Hotel Number of Rooms
And user Enter The Hotel Check in Date
And user Enter The Hotel Check out Date
And user Select The Hotel Adults per Room
And user Select The Hotl Children per Room
Then user Click On Search Button And It Navigates To The Select Hotel Page
 
Scenario: Search Select Hotel Page
When user Click On The Radio Button
Then user Click On Continue Button And It Navigates To The Book A Hotel

Scenario: Search Book A Hotel
When user Enter The Book A Hotel First Name
And user Enter The Book A Hotel Last Name
And user Enter The Book A Hotel Billing Address
And user Enter The Book A Hotel Credit Card No
And user Select The Book A Hotel Credit Card Type
And user Select The Book A Hotel Expiry Month
And user Select The Book A Hotel Expiry Year
And user Enter The Book A Hotel CVV Number
Then user Click On Book Now Button And It Navigates To The Booking Confirmation

Scenario: Search Booking Confirmation 
When user Click On Logout Button











